{
  "name": "RPlog_Let_the_Tour_Begin",
  "title": "Let the Tour Begin",
  "summary": "At the New Republic Embassy on Plaxton, the pregnant Ambassador Ambrosia Delgard hurries to finish dressing while her chrome protocol droid C4 greets the arriving Caspian delegation. The scarred warlord Lord Camrath Kizuka, accompanied by his bored Shistavanen adopted son Prince Ullan and a Praetorian honor guard, has come to receive New Republic Minister Leia Organa Solo on behalf of the absent Presav. Leia sweeps in with her own guard, exchanging gracious diplomatic courtesies with Kizuka and the over-eager Ullan as the two delegations merge their honor guards. The Ambassador arrives a touch late to welcome the Minister warmly, and Leia, with pointed good humor, notes the Presav's convenient absence and schedules the next annual inspection visit for a year hence. With pleasantries and veiled barbs exchanged, Leia asks for a look around, and Ambrosia gestures C4 to slip away and notify the Presav as the tour begins.",
